'''Guwahati Food Awards''' (GFA) is an annual [[Food awards|food award]] in [[India]], which was instituted in 2015. It aims to recognize superior services and achievements in the [[Food and Beverage]] industry of [[Guwahati]], India.<ref name="st''/><ref name="nm"/>
The winners gets selected through a multi-phase process that involves public voting, food tasting and the jury’s visits.<ref>{{cite news|title=Guwahati Food Awards’18 on March 23|url=http://www.assamtribune.com/scripts/mdetails.asp?id=mar1918/city054|publisher=[[The Assam Tribune]]|date=March 19, 2018}}</ref> ==History== It was established in 2015 by [[G Plus]].<ref name="nm"/> == Editions== === 2018 === This edition received over 157 nominations across 23 categories.<ref>{{cite news|last1=Sabyasachi|first1=Sharma|title=Guwahati food Awards presented to 33 winners|url=http://www.apnnews.com/category/foodbeverages/guwahati-food-awards-presented-to-33-winners-115722|publisher=APN News|date=March 24, 2017}}</ref> The jury of GFA 2018 includes Chef Faruk Ahmed, Dr. Geeta Dutta and Aabhishek Bedi Varma, a former chef of [[Taj Group |Taj Group of Hotels]] and headed by Suresh Hinduja, the CEO of Gourmet India.<ref>{{cite news|title=Guwahati Food Awards 2018|url=http://www.indigenousherald.com/index.php/news-alert/1805-guwahati-food-awards-2018|publisher=Indigenous Herald|date=March 24, 2018}}</ref> [[Kunal Vijaykar]] was a chief guest for the event.<ref>{{cite news|title=Actor Kunal Vijaykar to be chief guest for Guwahati Food Awards 2018|url=http://unitreed.com/food/actor-kunal-vijaykar-chief-guest-guwahati-food-awards-2018/|publisher=Unitreed.com|date=March 17, 2018}}</ref> ====Winners<ref name="st''>{{cite news|title=Guwahati Food Awards 2018 Winners Announced|url=http://www.theshillongtimes.com/2018/03/24/guwahati-food-awards-2018-winners-announced/|publisher=[[Shillong Times]]|date=March 24, 2018}}</ref> ==== {| class="wikitable" |- ! Category !! Winner's Name |- | Best Bakery (Chain)|| Loyans Bakery & Confectionery |- | Best Bakery (Single Outlet)|| Style O Cake |- | Best Cafeteria|| 11th Avenue Cafe Bistro |- | Best Club/Lounge|| Terra Mayaa |- | Best Fast Food Joint (Chain)|| J14 |- | Best Hangout Place|| The Steaming Mug |- | Best Mithai Shop|| Makhan Bhog |- | B